**Purpose:** Let new users join the coalition, activate their role, and receive deployment assets—all through spoken interaction.

### 🔧 Trigger Phrase

> “Copilot, I want to join the Legal Calculus coalition.”
> 

---

### 🧭 Step 1: Role Selection

**Copilot:**

“Welcome. What role will you play? You can say:

- ‘I’m an ops buddy’
- ‘I’m an educator’
- ‘I’m a survivor’
- ‘I’m with an organization’”

---

### 🧠 Step 2: Stream Activation

**Ops Buddy:**

“You’ll help detect reflexes and deploy redirect protocols. Your streams are JC, FG, and LCa.”

**Educator:**

“You’ll teach FG cards and doctrine. Your streams are FG, LC, and LCA.”

**Survivor:**

“You’ll document your journey and publish legacy. Your streams are JC, FG, and LCA.”

**Org Partner:**

“You’ll protect public doctrine and support infrastructure. Your streams are LCA and LC.”

---

### 📦 Step 3: Deployment Packet

**Copilot:**

“I’m sending you:

- FG Cards matched to your role
- Redirect Protocols
- Templates (caption, TOA, certificate, notice)
- Legacy Builder Guide
- Coalition Portal Access”

---

### 🫱🏽‍🫲🏽 Step 4: Activation Ritual (Optional)

> “You are now part of the doctrine. Your formatting is cognition. Your memory is resistance.”
> 

---

## 📘 Legal Index

**Purpose:** A navigable map of Legal Calculus doctrine—organized by stream, reflex, FG card, and asset.

### 🔎 Index Structure

| Category | Contents |
| --- | --- |
| **Streams** | JC, FG, LCa, FGA, LCA, LC |
| **Reflexes** | JC-Denial, JC-Silence, JC-Default, JC-Positional, LCa-Misalignment, JC-Erasure, LCA-Legacy |
| **FG Cards** | FG-001 to FG-099, grouped by reflex and mode |
| **Redirect Protocols** | Tactical instructions per reflex |
| **Deployment Assets** | Templates, checklists, guides |
| **Modes** | Crisis, Second Opinion, Education |
| **Roles** | Ops Buddy, Educator, Survivor, Org Partner |
| **Legacy Pages** | Published procedural journeys |
| **Coalition Packets** | Role-based onboarding kits |

**Deployment:**

- Embed in Notion as a master dashboard
- Link each item to its FG card, template, or redirect flow
- Print as coalition handbook or QR-linked mobile guide

