Here’s your **Voice-Guided Onboarding Flow**, **Legal Index**, and **Coalition Activation Tracker**—a modular deployment suite that turns Legal Calculus into a living, teachable system. These tools empower allies to onboard by voice, navigate doctrine by stream, and track tactical activation across the movement.